                            <comment id="12589391" author="jimk" created="Wed, 16 Apr 2008 01:56:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Right now in 0.2, the master waits for hdfs to exit safe mode and the region server waits forever or until it is killed trying to contact the master.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is there more we want to do for this issue (aside from fix the issues linked to this one)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12589632" author="stack" created="Wed, 16 Apr 2008 16:32:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on closing this issue as no longer relevant (IIRC, way back then, the regionserver was going down because HDFS was sick but this issue is missing that description so should be closed).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12589653" author="jimk" created="Wed, 16 Apr 2008 17:08:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I should also mention that the behavior of the Master and Region Server is the same on the 0.1 branch as it is on 0.2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If we find more startup issues we can open a new Jira for them.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
